# Burrow Base ‚Äî Homepage Copy Instructions

## Purpose
This document defines the exact copy structure, tone, and messaging for the Burrow Base homepage.

Burrow Base is:
- An installed digital operations manager
- Not software
- Not a DIY tool
- Not a website builder

Language must stay calm, minimal, and operational.

Never use ‚Ñ¢ anywhere on the site.

---

## GLOBAL COPY RULES (DO NOT BREAK)

- Simple sentences
- No hype
- No exaggerated claims
- No buzzwords
- No ‚ÄúAI-powered‚Äù language
- No feature dumping
- Focus on outcomes, not tools
- Assume the reader is busy and skeptical

Avoid words like:
‚ÄúRevolutionary‚Äù, ‚ÄúAll-in-one‚Äù, ‚ÄúGame-changing‚Äù, ‚ÄúScale fast‚Äù, ‚ÄúCrush‚Äù

Prefer:
‚ÄúHandled automatically‚Äù, ‚ÄúRuns quietly‚Äù, ‚ÄúNo action required‚Äù

---

## SECTION ORDER (LOCKED)

1. Hero
2. Who We Help
3. Digital Front Desk
4. Guarded Scheduling
5. Job Flow & Handoff
6. Payments & Follow-Up
7. Reputation & Owner Alerts
8. How It All Fits Together
9. Primary Call to Action

---

## 1. HERO SECTION

### Eyebrow
For contractors and service businesses

### Headline
Run your service business without running the office

### Subheadline
Burrow Base installs a digital operations manager that handles leads, scheduling, customer communication, payments, and reviews ‚Äî automatically.

### Primary CTA
See how it works

### Secondary CTA (optional)
Get a demo

### Trust Line
$297/month ¬∑ No contracts ¬∑ Cancel anytime

### Visual Direction (not copy)
- Clean background
- No photography
- One phone visual only
- No callouts or arrows

---

## 2. WHO WE HELP

### Section Title
Who We Help

### Intro Copy
Burrow Base is built for contractors and service businesses that want their day-to-day operations handled without adding staff or juggling tools.

If your business answers calls, schedules jobs, sends invoices, and depends on reviews ‚Äî this is for you.

### Cards

**General Contractors**  
Keep projects moving without chasing calls, follow-ups, or payments.

**Remodelers**  
Protect your schedule, handle inquiries automatically, and stay focused on the work.

**Service Businesses**  
HVAC, plumbing, electrical, cleaning, pressure washing, and more ‚Äî where missed calls mean lost jobs.

### Footer Line
Start with one system. Expand only when you need it.

---

## 3. DIGITAL FRONT DESK

### Section Title
Digital Front Desk

### Lead Line
Never miss a lead again.

### Body Copy

**Instant response, every time**  
When a call, text, or form comes in, the system responds automatically and keeps the conversation moving.

**Leads handled while you‚Äôre working**  
On a job site, driving, or with a customer ‚Äî incoming inquiries are acknowledged and guided forward.

**A calm, organized inbox**  
No call anxiety. No message pileups. Conversations stay clean and tracked.

**This replaces**  
Manually returning missed calls and hoping the lead didn‚Äôt move on.

---

## 4. GUARDED SCHEDULING

### Section Title
Guarded Scheduling

### Lead Line
Your calendar, protected by rules.

### Body Copy

**Built-in buffers and limits**  
Jobs are spaced properly. No double bookings. No impossible days.

**Automatic confirmations and reminders**  
Customers know exactly when you‚Äôre coming.

**Changes handled automatically**  
Reschedules and updates happen without back-and-forth.

**This replaces**  
Constant calendar checking and schedule chaos.

---

## 5. JOB FLOW & HANDOFF

### Section Title
Job Flow & Handoff

### Lead Line
Every job moves forward without friction.

### Body Copy

**Clear job stages**  
Leads, booked jobs, active work, and completed jobs are always visible.

**Automatic technician handoff**  
Job details, timing, and notes are delivered automatically.

**Owner stays out of the middle**  
Techs know what to do without asking.

**This replaces**  
Acting as dispatcher and repeating job details.

---

## 6. PAYMENTS & FOLLOW-UP

### Section Title
Payments & Follow-Up

### Lead Line
Get paid without chasing.

### Body Copy

**Invoices sent automatically**  
When the job is complete, the invoice goes out.

**Friendly payment reminders**  
Unpaid invoices follow up on their own.

**Clear visibility**  
Paid, unpaid, and overdue amounts at a glance.

**This replaces**  
Late invoices and awkward reminders.

---

## 7. REPUTATION & OWNER ALERTS

### Section Title
Reputation & Owner Alerts

### Lead Line
You‚Äôre notified only when it matters.

### Body Copy

**Automatic review requests**  
Happy customers are prompted without you asking.

**Private issue detection**  
Problems surface internally before going public.

**Exception-only alerts**  
If everything is handled, you hear nothing.

**This replaces**  
Manually asking for reviews and surprise bad feedback.

---

## 8. HOW IT ALL FITS TOGETHER

### Section Title
A Simple System. Installed for You.

### Body Copy
Burrow Base isn‚Äôt another tool to manage.

It quietly handles:
- Leads  
- Scheduling  
- Customer communication  
- Payments  
- Reviews  

So you can focus on the work ‚Äî not the office.

Start with one layer. Expand when you‚Äôre ready.

