## FINAL CHECKLIST

Before publishing:
- No ‚Ñ¢ anywhere
- No feature lists in hero
- No tool language
- All phone visuals share the same background style
- Tone feels calm, not salesy

If it feels impressive, it‚Äôs wrong.
If it feels obvious, it‚Äôs right.

The cell phone demo should be update to this " # Burrow Base ‚Äî Homepage Copy + Phone Demo Instructions

## PURPOSE
Defines homepage copy AND the unified phone visual system.

All phone demos must:
- Share the same shell
- Share the same screen background
- Differ only in content + animation

Never use ‚Ñ¢ anywhere.

---

## GLOBAL VISUAL RULES (PHONE DEMOS)

- No pure black backgrounds
- Soft depth, matte finish
- Subtle gradient only
- Calm, studio-lit feel
- No glow, no neon, no effects

---

## UNIFIED PHONE SHELL (USE EVERYWHERE)

### Replace all `.bb-phone`, `.bb-screen`, `.bb-notch`, and shadow styles with this.

```css
:root{
  --frameTop:#181a1f;
  --frameBot:#0e0f13;

  --screenTop:#151922;
  --screenMid:#10141c;
  --screenBot:#0b0e14;

  --card:#141821;
  --line:#262b36;

  --text:#f1f5f9;
  --muted:#9aa1ad;

  --accent:#2563eb;
  --success:#22c55e;
  --danger:#ef4444;

  --shadow:0 35px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
}

/* PHONE SHELL */
.bb-phone{
  width:340px;
  height:700px;
  border-radius:46px;
  background:
    linear-gradient(180deg,var(--frameTop),var(--frameBot));
  padding:14px;
  position:relative;
  box-shadow:var(--shadow);
}

/* INNER EDGE */
.bb-phone::after{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;
  inset:6px;
  border-radius:40px;
  box-shadow:
    inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.05),
    inset 0 18px 40px rgba(255,255,255,.03);
  pointer-events:none;
}

/* NOTCH */
.bb-notch{
  position:absolute;
  top:10px;
  left:50%;
  transform:translateX(-50%);
  width:150px;
  height:28px;
  background:#000;
  border-radius:0 0 18px 18px;
  z-index:5;
}

/* SCREEN */
.bb-screen{
  height:100%;
  border-radius:32px;
  background:
    radial-gradient(
      circle at top,
      rgba(255,255,255,.06),
      transparent 38%
    ),
    linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      var(--screenTop),
      var(--screenMid) 45%,
      var(--screenBot)
    );
  overflow:hidden;
  padding:26px 16px;
  color:var(--text);
}"

